WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.640 --> 00:00:04.300
Once you've identified that users
engage with your app infrequently or

00:00:04.300 --> 00:00:08.760
they've stopped using it entirely,
how do you re-engage those audiences?

00:00:08.760 --> 00:00:12.760
&gt;&gt; You can appeal to those users with
a variety of marketing strategies

00:00:12.760 --> 00:00:17.010
like push notification, email marketing,
and re-marketing campaigns.

00:00:17.010 --> 00:00:20.480
But remember, it's important to find
the golden path and not over do it.

